query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('11.10',
'12.10',
'compactness',
'dependencies',
'determinant',
'euclidean-geometry',
'graphing-functions',
'internet',
'network-manager',
'power-series',
'predicate-logic',
'python',
'scripts',
'triangles',
'virtualbox')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Caucus',
'Citizen Patrol',
'Commentator',
'Constituent',
'Excavator',
'Famous Question',
'Good Answer',
'Good Question',
'Notable Question',
'Student',
'Supporter',
'Teacher',
'Yearling') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
